Package boundary

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InvoiceUI
    Boundary class for the Invoice User Interface that allows staff to create invoices and generate revenue reports
    MainUI
    This boundary class provides users with access to different boundaries
    MemberUI
    This boundary class provides users with access to various functionalities of member management.
    MenuUI
    Boundary class for the Menu User Interface that allows staff to access menu information, methods to update menu items and generate the menu
    OrderUI
    This boundary class provides users with access to various functionalities of order management.
    ReservationUI
    This boundary class provides users with access to various functionalities of reservation management.
    TableUI
    Boundary class for the Table User Interface that allows staff to access table information, methods to udisplay occupied or unoccupied tables
